[quote=“stewie0888, post:2, topic:299882”]try this

Step 1. Create New Text Document

Step 2. Open the New Text Document

Step 3. Paste this in the New Text Document:

@echo off
Title Compiler
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_16\bin\javac.exe" *.java
pause

Step 4. Save as complierr.bat

Step 5. Move it to your Server Folder

Step 6. Run Complierr[/quote]

Actually it’s a Compiler, if above didn’t work try setting your environment variables, here’s the topic http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,375681.0.html
